 * 0.3.9a read and print gi parameter
 * 0.4a editor for Potential Models
 * 0.4.1a corrected pmOverwrite name Problem
 * 0.4.2a fixed pmbutton problem with savedialog
 * 0.5a import resultfiles -- 3rd release 5/2007
